lead_paragraph: With Stephen Strasburg not expected to pitch in the National League Division Series and Joe Ross not yet fully stretched out after a two-month layoff, the Washington Nationals are counting on Gio Gonzalez to come through in the playoffs.

headline.print_headline: Diamondbacks Beat Nationals in Rain-Shortened Game
